<para id="fs-id1592457">Now we have all the information we need from the problem! </para><para id="eip-id1170325057558">You multiply the number times the value to get the total value of each type of coin. While you do not know the actual number, you do have an expression to represent it.</para>
<para id="fs-id1785885">And so now multiply <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext mathvariant="italics">number</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mtext mathvariant="italics">value</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> and write the results in the Total Value column.</para>
