<para id="fs-id1600709">Step 4. <emphasis effect="bold">Translate</emphasis> into an <term>equation</term>. Restate the problem in one sentence. Then translate into an equation.<newline/>
<media id="fs-id1553938" alt="The sentence “Sum of the value of the dimes and value of the nickels is total value of the coins,” is written. Below “value of the dimes” is 0.10d. Below “and” is a plus sign. Below “value of the nickels” is 0.05(d plus 9). Below “is” is an equal sign. Below “total value of the coins” is 2.25.">
