<para id="fs-id1391205">Step 4. <emphasis effect="bold">Translate.</emphasis> Write the equation by adding the 'total value’ of all the types of coins.</para><para id="fs-id1876037">Step 5. <emphasis effect="bold">Solve</emphasis> the equation.<newline/>


<table id="eip-id1168468405585" class="unnumbered unstyled" summary="The top line says, “Write the equation.” Beside this is 0.25q plus 0.01(2q) equals 2.43. The next line says to multiply and shows 0.25q plus 0.02q equals 2.43. The next line says to combine like terms and shows 0.27q equals 2.43. The next line says to divide by 0.27 and shows q equals 9 quarters. The next line says that the number of pennies is 2q, then shows 2q followed by 2 times a red 9 equals 18 pennies."><label/>
