 </row>
 
</tbody>



</tgroup>
</table></para><para id="fs-id1577104">Step 6. <emphasis effect="bold">Check</emphasis> the answer in the problem.</para><para id="fs-id1778818">Maria has <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> quarters and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pennies. Does this make <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>$2.43</m:mtext><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-id1529449"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:mtext>9 quarters</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>0.25</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mn>2.25</m:mn></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mtext>18 pennies</m:mtext></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>0.01</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mspace width="0.1em"/><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mrow><m:mn>0.18</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mtext>_____</m:mtext></m:munder></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Total</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:mrow><m:mtext>$2.43</m:mtext><m:mo>✓</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-id1558428">Step 7. <emphasis effect="bold">Answer</emphasis> the question. Maria has nine quarters and eighteen pennies.</para></solution>
