<para id="fs-id1533121">Step 4. <emphasis effect="bold">Translate:</emphasis> Write the equation by adding the total value of all the types of coins.</para><para id="fs-id1879316">Step 5. <emphasis effect="bold">Solve</emphasis> the equation.</para>
